    Favorite piece from the collection

    I love the volume of those pants and the length, not very long like other wide leg denim pants. Besides, the fabric is soft, light and drapes nicely. I'm 5'4, they just hit my foot without touching the floor. Size 25 and 26 both works for me, but I'm keep 26 for the volume. That reminds me of a styl...e from Chanel preSpring last year. I also saw the same style in khaki in store, really don't like the fabric, the cotton look thin and cheap. I suggest getting those directly from Doen.
